description:
My place is close to Employees Only, Fat Cat, Buvette, Smalls Jazz Club, Joseph Leonard, Jeffrey Grocery, Liqueteria, Stumptown, 305 Fitness, Washington Square Park, Union Square, Subway lines: A,C,E,B,D,F,M,L,1,2,3. 

You’ll love my place because of the neighborhood, central location, close to parks and tons of restaurants, the comfy bed, private space, new bathroom and kitchen. My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, and business travelers. 4th floor walk-up.
